com.soen6441.core.tower

类 TowerManagerFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.soen6441.core.tower.TowerManagerFactory

  • public class TowerManagerFactory
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is used to define TowerManagers. This class uses singleton pattern. While the first time using this class, it will generate all kinds of TowerManagers and store them in a map. When there is a need to create or upgrade a tower, this class should be called first, in order to get a particular TowerManager.
